detaileddescription.para: Updates this Regression object by fetching the actual values of the ValueSupplier s and processing them. The ValueSupplier s are passed in the constructor of this Regression object. This update() method complies with the one described in DESMO, see [Page91].

detaileddescription.para: Implementation of the virtual update(Observable, Object) method of the Observer interface. This method will be called automatically from an Observable object within its notifyObservers() method. Whenever either of the two ValueSupplier objects providing the x or y value is updated and calling notifyStatistics() the x and the y value will be fetched and a new regression will be calculated.

parameterdescription.para: java.util.Observable : The Observable calling this method within its own notifyObservers() method.
